EN: The main language spoken in Cuba is Spanish.

ZH: 古巴有着丰富的文化遗产。
EN: Cuba has a rich cultural heritage.

ZH: 古巴的美食以黑豆和猪肉为主食。
EN: Traditional Cuban cuisine features black beans and pork.

ZH: 古巴的音乐和舞蹈在世界上很有名。
EN: Cuban music and dance are well-known around the world.

